----

This is a Black Highlighter theme based on the Sigma-9 [[[theme:night-rush-theme | Night Rush]]] theme by [[*user Nagiros]], with customized visuals for the [[[anomaly-classification-system-guide | ACS]]], [[[component:info-ayers | Info Bar]]], [[[component:toggle-sidebar-bhl | Toggle Sidebar]]], and [[[component:betterfootnotes | BetterFootnotes]]] components.

You will need to import the Black Highlighter theme in order to use this theme. [[[theme:black-highlighter-theme|To learn more go here]]].

On any wiki:

